{"componentChunkName":"component---src-page-post-tsx","path":"/speed-up-your-meetings-with-pre-written-meeting-minutes","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Markus Tacker","tagLine":"Software Crafter","description":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at Nordic Semiconductor.‚Äã\n\t\tMentor. Speaker. ‚ÄãConference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê","gitHubUrl":"https://github.com/coderbyheart/coderbyheart.com.git","siteUrl":"https://coderbyheart.com","twitter":"@coderbyheart","defaultCard":"https://images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/3Jk4P6nFPNzaz1gsguktk8/350b7e4ddb2c7d86416243d9902920e2/social-card-default-2020.png"}}},"pageContext":{"page":{"id":"ae76770a-e3b7-5589-9d1c-b5d5f1a267f7","name":"speed-up-your-meetings-with-pre-written-meeting-minutes","relativeDirectory":"post","relativePath":"post/speed-up-your-meetings-with-pre-written-meeting-minutes.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"When I joined "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"dotHIV"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://click4life.hiv/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" we had weekly "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"jour fixe"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\nmeetings via Google Hangout that easily took one hour with a team of five. Today\nwe barely ever break the 30 minute mark and no one has to keep tabs to create\nthe meeting minutes afterwards. Our meetings are fun again, productive for us\nand produce a well-made protocol afterwards."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#the-problem-with-our-old-meetings","ariaLabel":"the problem with our old meetings permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The problem with our "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"old"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" meetings"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"the-problem-with-our-old-meetings","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"We use our "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"jour fixe"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" meetings to get everyone up to speed on what's happening\nin all departments. At dotHIV that would be the work of the charitable\norganization, finances, marketing, sales, and development."},{"children":[],"tagName":"br","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\nOnce everyone was settled in we took turns in telling what we did in the last\nweek and provide an outlook for the coming week. With a five person team\neveryone would take up to 15 minutes recollecting "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"everything"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" that happened and\nanswer questions from the others as they came up‚Äìwhich would regularly spiral\noff into discussions. We tried to use timeboxes but this didn't work out very\nwell because there were so many exciting things going on during the week.\nEveryone is forced to listen to things that might not be relevant to him, which\nthey had prior knowledge about or they were just not capable of processing right\nnow because they were preoccupied."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"And then there was the one poor soul that had to make sense of everything and\nput it into writing because we wanted to have meeting minutes for ourselves and\nas a weekly report delivered to our extended team and the investors. I think you\nnow that writing meeting minutes for topics that you are not an expert for is\ncumbersome and produces a result that no one is really happy with."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#introducing-pre-written-meeting-minutes","ariaLabel":"introducing pre written meeting minutes permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Introducing: pre-written meeting minutes"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"introducing-pre-written-meeting-minutes","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The first thing I wanted to change was the time spent on "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"the telling part"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":". So\nI asked everyone to contribute a compact written summary to a Google Doc. I\nprovided a template with sections for every person. This report hat to be done\ntwo hours prior to our meeting so there would be enough time to read through the\nreport. Questions are added to the top of the document or as notes and we go\nthrough each one of them during the jour fixe."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"This is the intro text in our template:"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"We create the meeting minutes for our weekly Jour Fixe beforehand. Everyone\nreports what they deems noteworthy from their \"department\" until two hours\nbefore the meeting in a Google Doc. Keep it brief, this should be one or two\nsentences. If there is something to explain in detail, write it down in a\nseparate document. During the Jour Fixe we only talk about a topic, if someone\nhas a question about it! No reciting of topics most participants already know\nanyway. This is also the place to ask specific team members about their\ncommitment to a task. Commitments will then be added as task items in Trello."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"}],"tagName":"blockquote","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"What's great about this approach: the meeting minutes are done when the meeting\nstarts and during the meeting we can focus on the things that matter. We discuss\nthe open questions concerning the report and then we have a lot more time to\nsocialize, crack jokes and talk about the small things‚Äìwhich we couldn't before\nbecause we didn't have the time."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"}],"type":"root","data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Speed up your meetings with pre-written meeting minutes","subtitle":null,"noheadline":null,"date":"2015-03-09T09:00:00.000Z","abstract":"How to make your meetings fun again, productive and produce a well-made protocol afterwards.","lang":null},"headings":[{"id":"the-problem-with-our-old-meetings","depth":2,"value":"The problem with our old meetings"},{"id":"introducing-pre-written-meeting-minutes","depth":2,"value":"Introducing: pre-written meeting minutes"}]}},"Footer":{"id":"cfe5b9e2-511c-5615-992a-dab82e1f8ed7","name":"Footer","relativeDirectory":"","relativePath":"Footer.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Nordic Semiconductor"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://nordicsemi.com/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"."},{"children":[],"tagName":"br","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\nMentor. Speaker. Conference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2